<p>
If you like the <a href="/">Perl Weekly newsletter</a> it would be awesome if you could help spreading the word about it.
This can be done by sending one of the issues to a co-worker or a friend and recommending they <a href="/">subscribe</a>
to the newsletter. This can be done even without forwarding the newsletter just by sending a link and a recommendation.
</p>

